questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide discounts?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Definitely YES, best on your specifications.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What's Included in Website Management Service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It's Includes Management of your website from maintenance to error fix and adding products and taking care of all the issues and content. You do business and we will take care of all the online activity. Very reasonable Prices. Feel free to ask for further details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are there any demo websites you have designed already?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Of course! Yes, Just ask me via inbox and I'll send you my Portfolio to look at stunning webs, I've built by using different CMS, Builders & technologies.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What make this gig better than others?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I'm passionate to design a custom website for all businesses, as per their requirements. Graphic Design and Website Design is my hobby.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I need a responsive Godaddy website for all the devices, is it possible?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, our designed Godaddy website will be responsive for all kind of devices.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have a Godaddy Domain what I have to do now?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Great, if you have a Godaddy domain and Godaddy Hosting then we will set up an awesome clean and professional website for your business website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide content?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can with additional charges, I would create contents that effectively describes your business.
